HEADWORD: Lactoscope
<hw>Lac"to*scope</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>lac</ets>, <ets>lactis</ets> + <ets>scope</ets>.]</ety> <def>An
